  51:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_dma_ex.c ****       In order to reduce linked-list queue executing time and power consumption, the DMA channel su
  52:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_dma_ex.c ****       dynamic linked-list format. In fact, the DMA supports the execution of 2 types of linked-list
  53:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_dma_ex.c ****       dynamic.
  54:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_dma_ex.c **** 
